    <title>Anna, si douce.</title>
    <link href="http://www.n45.in/post/f4b0f6a4/"/>
    <id>http://www.n45.in/post/f4b0f6a4/</id>
    <published>2018-11-01T22:23:33.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-20T22:48:47.330Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="/assets/js/Meting.min.js"></script><p>「Anna-Varney Cantodea.」</p><hr><blockquote><p>灵魂在安娜的曲里翩翩起舞，<br>心上开出五彩的花。</p></blockquote><p align="right">2018.11.1日,于布拉格。</p>    <div id="aplayer-PoJMZpoP" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker"         data-id="4279447" data-server="netease" data-type="song" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="300px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#555"    ></div><p><em>Night of the Scarecrow</em> - SOPOR AETERNUS &amp; The Ensemble Of Shadows<br><em>Children of the Corn</em><br>℗ Apocalyptic Vision Records GmbH<br>Released on: 2003-01-27</p><hr><p>之前在读爱伦坡时，读到The Conqueror Worm，耳机里也正巧放到安娜的这首歌，仿佛歌与诗相互吸引。她的声音有能抚平一切哀伤的魔力，Alone(1)和Beautiful陪我度过了多少难过的日子。</p>    <div id="aplayer-kbizjDnC" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker"         data-id="27725388" data-server="netease" data-type="song" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="300px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#555"    ></div><p><em>The Conqueror Worm</em> - SOPOR AETERNUS &amp; The Ensemble Of Shadows<br><em>Poetica</em><br>℗ Apocalyptic Vision Records GmbH<br>Released on: 2013-09-19</p><hr><p>一次花了很长时间扒出Harvest Moon的谱子，改成了长笛二重奏。由于技术不佳，谱子格式和编排都不尽如人意。拿去给长笛老师看，想着一起吹，这支我很喜欢的曲子却在刚开头就被否定了。从此再没和别人说过这张谱子，对长笛的热情也渐渐淡了下来。<br>难过的是人和人不能总是心灵相通。</p>    <div id="aplayer-rMWEVzdj" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker"         data-id="4279458" data-server="netease" data-type="song" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="300px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#555"    ></div><p><em>Harvest Moon</em> - SOPOR AETERNUS &amp; The Ensemble Of Shadows<br><em>Children of the Corn</em><br>℗ Apocalyptic Vision Records GmbH<br>Released on: 2003-01-27</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
