  <entry>
    <title>Echos</title>
    <link href="http://www.n45.in/post/120fb5bf/"/>
    <id>http://www.n45.in/post/120fb5bf/</id>
    <published>2018-07-15T19:54:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-20T22:48:47.328Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="/assets/js/Meting.min.js"></script><p>「夜晚的海是我心中最浪漫的风景。遥远的梦在星星闪烁的地方，而海的尽头有我所爱的人们。」</p><hr><blockquote><p>任何词汇都无法形容这张专辑的灿烂。<br>在我心中<em>Echos</em>属于夜晚的海，最合拍的伴奏是永不停息的涛声。<br>她是呼唤风暴的战歌， 是繁星闪烁着的遥远的天边，是远洋的召唤。<br>我愿用我渺小而平凡的生命拥抱面前无边的黑暗，我愿向这海踏上没有归路的旅程，梦会指引我向光明。</p></blockquote><p align="right">2018.7.15日晚，日照。</p>    <div id="aplayer-yUKWkmzx" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker"         data-id="1537382" data-server="netease" data-type="album" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="300px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#555"    ></div><p><em>Echos</em> - Lacrimosa<br>℗ 2003 Hall of Sermon<br>Released on: 2003-01-27</p><hr><p>记得上一次是2018.3，当时在菲律宾的Bauan Divers Sactuary Resort潜店的岸边，正值中午，耳机里放着<em>Malina</em>，突然晴空遁入黑夜，海面巨浪滔天。<br>第一次感受到音乐能改变天象。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
